headline: Vulcan’s Earnings Are Dragging Down Construction Materials Stocks.
summary: FEATURE  Things are getting better for the construction materials company Vulcan Materials but not as much as investors expected. That is pressuring stocks elsewhere in the sector. On Tuesday, Vulcan reported fourth-quarter earnings per share of $1.
